headline: VideoAmp and Warner Bros. Discovery Sign Multi-Year Deal to Advance Measurement and Currency Innovation
summary: NEW YORK, July 24, 2025--Today, VideoAmp, a leading advertising technology company, announced a multi-year agreement with Warner Bros. Discovery, Inc. (Nasdaq: WBD) to expand their longstanding relationship and continue delivering currency optionality to the advertising marketplace.
